        {
            "title": "天文台｜早晚有一兩陣微雨 日間最高氣溫約17度 吹清勁偏東風",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ad60992ea7a6234a4ad169079f96f2c9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022207082492155.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股清勁至強風程度的東北季候風正影響廣東沿岸。同時，一道雲帶覆蓋該區及南海北部。本港今早天氣清涼，各區氣溫普遍在15度左右。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲，早晚有一兩陣微雨。日間最高氣溫約17度。吹清勁偏東風，離岸及高地間中吹強風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望明日漸轉吹偏北風，稍後氣溫下降，星期一早上市區最低氣溫約13度左右。下週中期雲量增多，有幾陣雨，氣溫稍為回升。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054233/即時-港聞-天文台-早晚有一兩陣微雨-日間最高氣溫約17度-吹清勁偏東風",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-22 07:11:24",
