            "title": "意甲│近期入局早 國際米蘭「主勝」趁「熱」買",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"國米入局甚早，有望半場前攻陷對手。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5917849cecf33e6ed631ad25285d318e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250221/_2025022121160685391.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">國米入局甚早，有望半場前攻陷對手。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h3>足智彩球賽編號：FB7923<br/>\n國際米蘭 VS 熱拿亞<br/>\nHOY App周日凌晨3:45直播<br/>\n推介：半場讓球[-0.5/-1]主勝</h3>\n<p>意甲尾場有國際米蘭主場迎戰熱拿亞，主隊對上兩場分別0:1僅負祖雲達斯及2:1力挫費倫天拿，不過半場前都分別以13對7次及10對3次攻門佔盡優勢，入局甚早。客軍熱拿亞同期則只對下半版的威尼斯及拖連奴，然而此兩場都未能半場取得入球，半場讓球讓半球/一球的「主勝」機會極大。\n\n</p><div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -124px; top: -12px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
